   You might be able to get the effect you want by turning <NoFeedBack> on 
and off.  So items that want the screen cleared have <nfb 0> in them and 
ones that do not want the screen cleared have <nfb> in them.  Note, you 
still want <ClearFeedback> in the parameter line.

